Nb5.} 9. O-O {[%cal Gg7a1,Bc3b5,Gb5c7][%csl Rc7] White castles Kingside in this 
specific position to avoid the open g7-a1 diagonal, and to have the immediate 
option of Nb5.} Qxc5 10. Nb5 {[%cal Gb5c7][%csl Rc7]} a6 (10... Na6 {is 
possible, but can be answered by} 11. Be5 {followed by Bd4.}) 11. Nc7 {[%csl 
