15. O-O-O {[%cal Gd1d5,Gc3d5][%csl Rd5,Ge2] This is roughly equal. On the plus 
side White currently has a better structure and a Bishop vs. a Knight. With 
pawns on both sides of the board any endgames could well favour White.} *

