the pawn with} 13. Qg7 {.}) 12. O-O {[%cal Bf1d1,Bd1d2,Ba1d1][%csl Re8] White 
has everything out and Black will still struggle to get his King safe. The next 
step would be to take control of the d-file with Rfd1, Rd2 and Rad1.} *

