4. e5 {[%csl Rf6] Simple and good.} Ne4 5. Nxe4 dxe4 6. Ne2 {[%cal 
Be2g3,Bg3e4,Bc2c3][%csl Rc6,Rc7] This is much better for White. The pawn on e4 
will probably drop with Ng3 at some point. Black would love to play ...c5 here 
but can't because of the misplaced c6-Knight.} *

