Be1g1,Bd1d3,Ba1d1,Bh1e1,Gd4e5,Gf4e5][%csl Rc8,Ge5] The prospects are roughly 
even. White will castle short, develop his Queen, centralise his Rooks preparing 
for the key battleground which in this position is in the centre.} *

